                            The application of the Opas Strategy is incredibly simple. Using a strategy simply means to follow a set of rules, which is exactly what we do. We apply a rigorously tested algorithm that indicates the top 25 stocks from the Opas Strategy from a database of 4000 companies and we purchase the top 25 companies every month. Which we then hold for a maximum of 12 months before selling.
                        </p>
