                                <li><strong>Yearly Review:</strong> When the following month arrives. We sell the previous year's portfolio – with a twist: we only sell stocks not part of the new year's selection, ensuring you stay invested in potential winners.</li>
                                <li><strong>Repeat and Reap:</strong> This cycle repeats monthly, 12 times a year. As you follow our guidance, you start selling and taking returns monthly, reinvesting in the new year's portfolios</li>
